{"type":"message","id":"04a515a2","parentId":"fbc2c2ea","timestamp":"2026-04-03T19:13:31.930Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"toolu_01BcLyBwUAzTBXdTqJaG1qpY","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.4.1 (da64a97) — Give me a workspace and I'll give you fewer tabs, fewer toggles, and more oxygen.\r\n\r\nUsage: openclaw agents [options] [command]\r\n\r\nManage isolated agents (workspaces + auth + routing)\r\n\r\nOptions:\r\n  -h, --help    Display help for command\r\n\r\nCommands:\r\n  add           Add a new isolated agent\r\n  bind          Add routing bindings for an agent\r\n  bindings      List routing bindings\r\n  delete        Delete an agent and prune workspace/state\r\n  list          List configured agents\r\n  set-identity  Update an agent identity (name/theme/emoji/avatar)\r\n  unbind        Remove routing bindings for an agent\r\n\r\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/agents"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":3879,"aggregated":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.4.1 (da64a97) — Give me a workspace and I'll give you fewer tabs, fewer toggles, and more oxygen.\r\n\r\nUsage: openclaw agents [options] [command]\r\n\r\nManage isolated agents (workspaces + auth + routing)\r\n\r\nOptions:\r\n  -h, --help    Display help for command\r\n\r\nCommands:\r\n  add           Add a new isolated agent\r\n  bind          Add routing bindings for an agent\r\n  bindings      List routing bindings\r\n  delete        Delete an agent and prune workspace/state\r\n  list          List configured agents\r\n  set-identity  Update an agent identity (name/theme/emoji/avatar)\r\n  unbind        Remove routing bindings for an agent\r\n\r\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/agents","cwd":"C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775243611912}}
