cle</b></mark> events \\(start, end, error\\) automatically\r\n- [Agent Workspace](https://docs.openclaw.ai/concepts/agent-workspace) - <mark><b>Agent</b></mark> Workspace\r\n- [Sub-Agents](https://docs.openclaw.ai/tools/subagents) - Sub-<mark><b>Agent</b></mark>s\r\n- [Default AGENTS.md](https://docs.openclaw.ai/reference/AGENTS.default) - Default <mark><b>AGENT</b></mark>S.md\r\n- [agent](https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/agent) - <mark><b>agent</b></mark>\r\n- [agents](https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/agents) - auth + routing\\). Related: Multi-<mark><b>agent</b></mark> routing: Multi-<mark><b>Agent</b></mark> Routing <mark><b>Agent</b></mark> workspace:\r\n- [Agent Bootstrapping](https://docs.openclaw.ai/start/bootstrapping) - <mark><b>Agent</b></mark> Bootstrapping\r\n- [Agent Send](https://docs.openclaw.ai/tools/agent-send) - <mark><b>Agent</b></mark> Send","cwd":"C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775243624442}}
